reviewText: Cover would make you think Bruce Lee is on all 9 movies.  THAT IS NOT THE CASE!  This is a pack of b movies from back in the day.  You will not get the kung fu you are thinking when you hear Bruce Lee.  You will get confuse on how bad the acting is and how people were paid good money to do these crap-hole-movies.
Problem free transaction, fast shipping, good deal too! Thanks!
This has nothing to do with bruce lee....bucnh of other movies.
I didn't like it. It had nothing in it with Bruce Lee. I sent it back. A very poor movie, I was very disappointed
Only one of the movies had bruce lee in it. .. and we expected the bruce lee movie pack to have bruce lee in it. .. my husband was very disappointed
I have no idea why Bruce Lee's picture is on the cover, because this set is NOT a Bruce Lee collection.
There are NO Bruce Lee movies on this DVD set??!!!!
These are NOT Bruce Lee movies.

Bruce Lee is not in any of the movies on the DVD.  OK, they did use clips of him fighting in "Fist of Fear, Touch of Death," but that movie was released years after his death.  If you want Bruce Lee films look elsewhere.
Not what I wanted and was very disappointed.
